{"type": "article", "id": 18993, "title": "沙漏盆景", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-14T07:40:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 134, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702134740pgmywcirWQFtNvA0.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这颗盆景是罩在沙漏型的容器里，使得倒进去的水会顺着中间很细的管道滴下去，以此来控制浇灌的量和速度，是非常巧妙的装置。而玻璃瓶的侧面的漏孔则用来帮助呼吸的，可以将新鲜空气释放房间里。来自澳大利亚的设计师 Xindong (Jonathan) Che，沙漏的外形很有梦幻气息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145715YuVmAnxHEbLs2vwl.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"733\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.69809524\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145716iRNj3M9DoThJA67g.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1366\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.26481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}